{"id":232878844,"title":"變額萬能壽險問題","content":"想問各位一下，最近剛好去元大開戶，沒有業配！！\n\n剛好業務就來推銷一下他們的萬能險，說是自己可以選擇標的（我會選擇IVV或S&P500）預估年化報酬率6%等等等等\n\n然後一個月投入7000元（本來叫我投入1萬的），大約50年後能領到1000萬XDD，以下附圖，看到我68歲那邊\nhttps://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/eeb73f6c-dfae-44df-8cc2-1d49b62cebc8/1280.jpeg\n\n重點來了，我一個月大約會有25000～30000拿去投資，4年內不會有重大改變，未來工作穩定6萬5起跳，我相信美股年化6%絕不是問題，是想問一下有沒有什麼建議，像是7000太多～太少之類的，還是根本直接買就好，不用用保險的方式買等等...希望大家能給個建議，非常感謝，以下是我的保單\nhttps://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/dd24bb91-9b60-4dfe-b8e5-3582bda86477/1280.jpeg","excerpt":"想問各位一下，最近剛好去元大開戶，沒有業配！！，剛好業務就來推銷一下他們的萬能險，說是自己可以選擇標的（我會選擇IVV或S&P500）預估年化報酬率6%等等等等，然後一個月投入7000元（本來叫我投入","anonymousSchool":false,"anonymousDepartment":true,"pinned":false,"forumId":"3bceb81c-574e-4a96-8050-4df56096d0df","replyId":null,"createdAt":"2020-01-12T14:28:56.807Z","updatedAt":"2020-01-12T14:28:56.807Z","commentCount":8,"likeCount":2,"tags":[],"topics":["壽險","投資","理財","保險","美股"],"supportedReactions":null,"withNickname":false,"reportReason":"","hiddenByAuthor":false,"meta":{"layout":"classic"},"forumName":"理財","forumAlias":"money","school":"中央警察大學","replyTitle":null,"gender":"M","personaSubscriptable":false,"reactions":[{"id":"286f599c-f86a-4932-82f0-f5a06f1eca03","count":2}],"hidden":false,"customStyle":null,"isSuspiciousAccount":false,"layout":"classic","withImages":true,"withVideos":false,"media":[{"url":"https://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/eeb73f6c-dfae-44df-8cc2-1d49b62cebc8/1280.jpeg"},{"url":"https://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/dd24bb91-9b60-4dfe-b8e5-3582bda86477/1280.jpeg"}],"reportReasonText":"","mediaMeta":[{"id":"30c3ba61-f100-4e78-9dc3-e93d6e21c7db","url":"https://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/eeb73f6c-dfae-44df-8cc2-1d49b62cebc8/640.jpeg","normalizedUrl":"https://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/eeb73f6c-dfae-44df-8cc2-1d49b62cebc8/640.jpeg","thumbnail":"https://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/eeb73f6c-dfae-44df-8cc2-1d49b62cebc8/640.jpeg","type":"image/thumbnail","tags":[],"createdAt":"2020-01-12T14:28:56.807Z","updatedAt":"2020-01-12T14:28